title: Building a Self, Ethics, and Client Boundaries
description:
How do you build a sense of self? Dr. Kirk Honda and Bob answer this question along with talking about ethical issues and if it's okay to show your therapist a text exchange with your spouse.

The Psychology In Seattle Podcast.

March 27, 2019.

Email: Contact@PsychologyInSeattle.com
